faculty of Arts and Sciences.

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:33.550
Eugene is the Abby Aldrich
Rockefeller Professor

00:05:33.550 --> 00:05:37.180
of Asian Arts in the FAS, as
well as a former Radcliffe

00:05:37.180 --> 00:05:38.470
Fellow.

00:05:38.470 --> 00:05:41.240
I'm delighted to have
both of them here today.

