00:15:54.380 --> 00:15:55.610
into other languages--

00:15:55.610 --> 00:15:56.650
French, Italian.

00:15:56.650 --> 00:15:59.374
- [SPEAKING CHINESE]

00:15:59.374 --> 00:16:01.040
- And then from that
language translated

00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:03.800
into German and other languages.

00:16:03.800 --> 00:16:12.980
- [SPEAKING CHINESE]

00:16:12.980 --> 00:16:15.770
- And then into
Japanese and other types

00:16:15.770 --> 00:16:20.870
of languages, so basically just
endless series of translation

00:16:20.870 --> 00:16:23.430
and then at the very
